Use Case
	Asteroid Collission w ship
Actors
	Ship, System,Asteroid
Description
	The system has tried to move Ship and is now seeing if ship has collided with asteroid.
	
Main Course of Events
Ship		System		Asteroid
			1.Ask for ship position and size
2.Provide them
			3.Ask each asteroid for position and size
						4.Provide them
			4.Calculate distance between the ship and each asteroid.
			5.See if any distance is greater than the ship size plus current asteroid size
			6.Continue moving ship
Alternative Flow of Events
5. The distance is not greater than. Declare game over.